
- copy httpd-perl.conf.example to ~/conf/extras/httpd-perl.conf and
  ensure it's being loaded in ~/conf/httpd.conf

- You need to install

  Apache
  mod_perl
  Geo::IP (www.maxmind.com)
  LWP::Simple - CPAN
  DateTime - CPAN
  XML::XPath - CPAN
  SVN::Client - use  sudo yum install subversion-perl
  HOP::Parser - CPAN
  HOP::Lexer - CPAN

- Set up and SVN user for the rules repository
  -- make sure it starts automatically (use chkconfig)
